---
import TestimonialCard from '../ui/TestimonialCard.astro';
import { Image, getImage } from 'astro:assets';

import glove_img from '@assets/glove_bullet.png';
import bg_img from '@assets/main_boxing_bg_opacity.png';

const optimizedBackground = await getImage({ src: bg_img });

const testimonials= [
  {
    quote: "\"My experience training with Ken was enlightening. Having trained casually before, I had accumulated a collection of bad habits that prevented me from striking to my full potential. Ken was very knowledgeable and identified the problem almost immediately. With his tutelage, I improved my form and power within my first visit!\"",
    name: "Christopher W.",
    role: "",
    image: glove_img,
    ringColor: "ring-light-tan-dark"
  },
];
---

<section class="py-24 bg-neutral-400">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div
          class="bg-[image:var(--bg-image)] bg-cover bg-center w-full"
          style={`--bg-image: url(${optimizedBackground.src});`}
        >
      


      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 mb-4 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full bg-light-tan-dark text-brown">
        Client Success Stories
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-brown">
        Results Backed by <span class="gradient-text">Experience</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify text-brown-light">
        With 20 years boxing and over 40 years teaching martial arts, Kanata Boxing brings the sweet
        science to Kanata and Stittsville where you will definitely learn to move like a butterfly and sting
        like a bee in our fun dynamic workouts while you:
      </p>
      <br>

      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl p-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4">
            <ul>
              <li>
                <Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-6 w-auto"
                  width={32}
                  height={32}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Get Fitter
              </li>
              <li>
                <Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-6 w-auto"
                  width={32}
                  height={32}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Gain Confidence
              </li>
              <li><Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-6 w-auto"
                  width={32}
                  height={32}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Reduce Stress
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4">
            <ul>
              <li><Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-6 w-auto"
                  width={32}
                  height={32}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Gain More Energy</li>
              <li><Image 
                  src={glove_img}
                  alt="Boxing Glove"
                  class="inline h-6 w-auto"
                  width={32}
                  height={32}
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                /> Build Self-Esteem</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      

      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl p-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">
          {testimonials.map((testimonial) => (
            <TestimonialCard testimonial={testimonial} variant="home" />
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <br>

      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify text-brown-light">
        The great thing about boxing is that anyone can do it regardless of your
        physicality and where, like all martial arts/combat sports it takes years to
        master the subtle nuances, it is the one combat sport where, as a beginner,
        you will see the fastest improvements and has easiest introduction where right
        from your first class you will feel like “Rocky” where our main goal is to help
        you feel better, healthier and more energetic.
      </p>
      <br>

      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify text-brown-light">
        If you're looking to improve your fitness, confidence and destress in a fun and
        supportive environment then our beginner-friendly boxing programs in Kanata
        and Stittsville's only stand-alone boxing program is the place for you.
      </p>
      <br>

      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify text-brown-light">
        Our Children's Boxing program is all about having fun, getting them use to
        exercising while developing hand-eye coordination, balance, concentration,
        agility, confidence and self-esteem leading to a more self-assured child that
        will help with their attention to their schoolwork and be calmer at home!
      </p>
      <br>
      
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify text-brown-light">
        Our Youth Boxing Program is all about giving them the “action” that this age
        groups need. Getting them busy with a fun cool activity that will make them
        look forward to the next session. Getting them to burn off excess energy and
        frustration while getting stronger, fitter and more agile in our dynamic
        cutting-edge workouts!!
      </p>
      <br>
      
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify text-brown-light">
        Our Adult Boxing Program helps you regain energy, stay active for years to
        come, and enrich your lifestyle. Don't worry if you're not in shape—that's
        exactly what our dynamic boxing program is for. We'll help you get moving
        again and feel fitter in no time. As Dr. Kenneth Cooper said, “You don't stop
        working out because you get old; you get old when you stop working out.”
        Think of it this way: if squatting, running, or jumping feels difficult at 40, what
        will it feel like at 60? If you already feel that way, we're here to help. With years
        of experience helping people reach their fitness goals, we're committed to
        getting you back in action, feeling fitter, happier, and we become invested in
        your success.
      </p>
      <br>
      
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-justify text-brown-light">
        There is no set schedule to give as we schedule your sessions around your
        availability with small group sessions capped at 4 or even one on one sessions
        where in both instances, your progress is personally monitored!
      </p>
      

    </div>
    </div>

    
  </div>
</section>
